cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and neural network architectures, which are typically covered in the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The use of word embeddings and attention mechanisms further supports these categories.
